profile: G.E. Quast Excavating Ltd., was established in 1980 by owner Garry Quast to provide excavation, snow services, septic systems and cartage. During these past 30 years Garry has proudly maintained the reputation of being a trusted member of the local community as well as a gainfull employer of local talent. Together, with son Eddie, and their reliable team they continue to proudly serve the ever growing Ottawa Valley with the highest level of safety, integrity and mechanical aptitude needed to ensure our customers both new and old receive quality, cost effective workmanship from project execution to completion.
